  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This survey is conducted for preparing application material for re-examination under the
      Pharmaceutical Affairs Law and its Enforcement Regulation; its aim is to reconfirm the
      clinical usefulness of COZAAR XQ through collecting the safety and efficacy information
      according to the Re-examination Regulation for New Drugs.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
